ubbles，通常都係Champaign or sparkling wine都常用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都可以用嚟封住啲蘇打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618f134bcb5a0b8b5bb31574c5d8da5cc2a8376a","tid":2373431,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6b8f1f0ab6adf6ebba7bb59a3e406671e0a7a5a","tid":2373431,"uid":301627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"之前就做過餐飲<br />\n紅酒通常擺室溫嘅，好似開盖後擺3-5日之內都應該ok，擺一星期有突嘅話會有少少變味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我無試過，不過聽同事講陣味會變到似變味嘅利賓納<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白酒放雪櫃就通常都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過最好10日內清走佢。保鮮紙就係用嚟封口以防啲酒無曬bubbles，通常都係Champaign or sparkling wine都常用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都可以用嚟封住啲蘇打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"白酒唔放雪櫃可以嗎?"},{"pid":"cf15eca59228a2de879e2bfb98761bd1fd6b9e1a","tid":2373431,"uid":301627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"618f134bcb5a0b8b5bb31574c5d8da5cc2a8376a","tid":2373431,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6b8f1f0ab6adf6ebba7bb59a3e406671e0a7a5a","tid":2373431,"uid":301627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"之前就做過餐飲<br />\n紅酒通常擺室溫嘅，好似開盖後擺3-5日之內都應該ok，擺一星期有突嘅話會有少少變味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我無試過，不過聽同事講陣味會變到似變味嘅利賓納<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h